an attitude of goodwill to somebody that they're going to you know uh huggy huggy wuggy you all the time sometimes people are cruel sometimes people say nasty things sometimes we do nasty things and yet you still have to have that sort of goodwill um often i think uh in a relationship um you know there's um there's a sort of uh

84
00:08:56,032 --> 00:09:02,861
underlying resentment that grows because somebody is not being as generous as you are.

85
00:09:03,023 --> 00:09:15,240
