92
00:09:39,876 --> 00:09:41,618
That means you want to control them.

93
00:09:41,638 --> 00:09:51,267
Now, that doesn't mean to say that what they're doing is skillful or is wholesome, but the anger is not necessary because the anger is manifesting your desire to control them.

94
00:09:52,072 --> 00:10:03,283
And as soon as you realize that, you sort of just wait or go out of the room for a little while, go for a walk, count 10, and then come back.

95
00:10:03,864 --> 00:10:10,789
And when you're coming from a place of non-aggression, then of course there's the ability to discuss something.

96
00:10:12,152 --> 00:10:18,957
It doesn't mean to say that at times we can't be assertive, direct,

97
00:10:19,293 --> 00:10:24,077
But the anger really builds up a bad energy between people.

98
00:10:24,477 --> 00:10:27,221
And if it's not resolved, it remains there as resentment.

99
00:10:27,260 --> 00:10:30,384
