and uh generosity so generosity is the ability the ability to give i mean that's what it is and um whenever the buddha's talking to lay people he always starts with generosity he even points out that thieves can be generous having having saved a thousand pounds for you he might give it to needy people in his family and so on so uh generosity is uh just that basic willingness to share uh of your wealth

